               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Ms. contains only one text:
 I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnna “Book of the
                     Christening” (fols. 2r-37r)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2r" to="37r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1940Mashaf">Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā (General record)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez" type="embedded"><locus target="#2r">2r</locus>መጽሐፈ፡ ጥምቀት፡</incipit>
                     <note>- Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā is called Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat in the incipit (<locus target="#2r">2r</locus>) and in <ref target="#a1">Additio 1</ref>.</note>


                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
